Text:
I have downloaded the file sucessfully, but when I try to install a game and put the name and serial info to crack the game, it doesn't work. I get a message: "The programme is not responding".

What can I do?
I have also installed with no joy?

Before installing the games, disable the internet connection. If no, the games connect to gamehouse.com and won't accept any code created with the keygen.It happend with 2 games to me. Without internet all works great 100%.

The prior message was correct - you MUST disable your internet connection prior to entering your keygen codes.  If you enter the codes while you are connected to the internet, the codes entered after will not work, even if you are disconnected.  You will have to delete the keys from the registry to 'reset' the ability to enter the codes.
This version is better GameHouse Games Collection 2005.12 (150 Games) CD1 & CD2 [Shadow] www.isohunt.com Dont need to copy and paste each key :) but still needs offline install.
For what its worth JewelQuest and Tradewinds keygens were detected as trojans.
